      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 342
    },
    {
      "text": "We all know what's going on and we're just gonna, woo.",
      "start": 843,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 343
    },
    {
      "text": "So anyway, that's why y'all are here.",
